Class AccountManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • bankmanager.AccountManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    class AccountManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Account Manager handles all requests relating to Account delegated from Bank Manager.
